plot: Before the Ireland excursion begins, Melissa hosts a Boujie Kidz pop-up for Danielle, who reveals how blindsided she feels by Rachel's rat behavior. Paul's family gives Dolores advice on how to handle drama in the Emerald Isle. Jennifer and Bill make plans to continue improving their relationship when she returns. Once they've crossed the pond, Teresa's bachelorette party begins. Jennifer is pressed to reveal her involvement in the coffee readings before Danielle presses her again, this time over the secrets Marge's ex-friend revealed to her. Once the tea is spilled, Danielle regrets ever asking at all.—Anonymous
